Package: TreeMatching
Type: Package
Title: Matching of Individual Trees in Forest Plot Inventories
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Jean-Romain", "Roussel", email = "info@r-lidar.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Tools for matching individual trees between forest plot inventories. 
    Provides 3D matching strategies based on spatial coordinates and DBH or height
    dimensions using different matching strategies.
